{"title":"三亩棉苗一片心","authors":["华银岳"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":4,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"三亩棉苗一片心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浙江慈溪社员　华银岳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴家五队风格高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大力支援好棉苗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我队缺苗得帮助，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉花种足又种好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话说六月是三号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我队社员去补苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发现长三亩纯白地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立时心如滚油浇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友定低头不讲话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"官章拼命头皮搔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是官夫提醒我："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“快到五队跑一跑！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我忽然想起事一件，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五队确实有余苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队长出门开会前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经和我谈论到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔脚就走到五队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开口就把来意表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五队社员正摘豆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一听要苗脸带笑："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你队我队都一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快带人来掘苗。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带得喜讯回队里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个社员迷迷笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟我一路而行步生风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来回三里歌满道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你掘我挑一整天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半块白地披绿袍；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二天又去十五个人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长三亩满地是新苗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看了自己看人家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五队地里象蜂巢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千疮百孔操作难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豆子碰落也不少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我开口就问五队长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工肥补贴需多少？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那晓得五队长批了我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们不是为钞票，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互相支援望大家好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种得棉花超指标，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就算大家有功劳。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他话儿不多情意重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无私相助风格高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我队到底怎么办？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家想出三大条——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一送肥田粉二十五斤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二写稿子去登报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三下决心学五队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友谊竞赛把战挑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三件大事商量好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众人推我做代表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这倒难住了我会计华银岳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这千重情意如何表？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}